    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato </strong>and <strong>drained chickpeas </strong>to the pot with the<strong> vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> </strong>a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the sweet potato is fork-tender, stirring occasionally – this is your <strong>spiced sweet potato & chickpea stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
