    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the stew is cooking, add your <strong>couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, the <strong>remaining vegetable stock mix </strong>and your <strong>sultanas</strong></p><p>Stir it all together, then cover and set aside until all of the stock has been absorbed</p><p>Fluff with a fork before serving – this is your <strong>sultana couscous</strong></p>",
